snippet.title: Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals DLC Showcase 01 - MONSTRUM | Hosted by SuperHorrorBro
snippet.description:
Get the Monsters & Mortals: Monstrum  DLC on Steam on Dec 21st!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1450740/Monsters__Mortals__Monstrum
Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals is available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266690/Dark_Deception_Monsters__Mortals

Follow SuperHorrorBro's channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChL4WU9YLlxXXNSwlzM1-7g

Video edited by Mike Bambridge (SuperHorrorBro)
Monstrum DLC music composed by Daniel Dombrowsky
(Original Monstrum OST tracks composed by Jaime Cross)
